texts.text: I need to find Nyarlathotep...!

*Scream*
Monsters here too?!
There! It still hurts, but you need to just bear it, Honey...!
*Gasp*
>Honey trips while wading through a sea of people.
Ow... Don't stop, Honey. You're everybody's last hope.
You have to do something about this...!

*Laugh*
Nm? This is... Water...?
Ah, yes. Humans shed tears when they laugh heartily.
Such a strange body. It cries when it feels sorrow, joy and pain.
There you are!
*Roar*
*Wince*
Finally caught up to you, Nyarlathotep!

*Snicker*
Did I get too careless?
This farce has been much too delightful.

*Pant*
And this is your punishment...!
>As Honey successfully lands her attacks,
>the people that were turned into demons begin returning to normal.
Y-You're a person?! You're not a monster...?!
Y-You too...! I thought you definitely were a monster!

Vince?!
Newbie?!
Wait, wasn't I just fighting against demons...?
You guys?! Hey, what the hell's going on here...?!
I don't know.
Where's Honey?
Hey, can you guys hear me?!
Honey! Where were you this whole time?! You okay?!

*Wince*
Honey's just... Fine...!
Honey, what's going on?! You fighting someone?!

Yes!
Take this...!
My hands are full right now, but I need you to listen...!
A demon called Nyarlathotep made everyone look like demons!
What?!
Its spell turned people into demons and demons into people!
And it made us all turn on each other... Bastard!
So the little kid that stabbed me in the back was a demon...
But others looked completely normal!
That's right! Not everyone was affected by the spell!
Dammit. This thing means business.
And there's no easy solution. This thing's illusion's meant to spread chaos.
Ugh...!
Honey!! Hold on! Tell me where you are!
By West Shinjuku...
Honey needs to focus on fighting now so, bye!
Y'all get that...?!
Copy!
Everyone, get to Honey's position ASAP!
If Honey doesn't take down Nyarlathotep now,
this world might sink even deeper into chaos.

This world?
Not just Tokyo?
I've been seeing it on the news in other countries lately.
Demons running around and causing people to panic.
Then we need to stop them! That means my home is in danger as well!
Yo, we're in the same boat as you. If that illusion takes over our minds again...
We ain't gonna be able to tell each other apart...
I can at least tell girls apart by how they smell...
But that might be hard if they're some gross demon...
That'd be a pretty big turn off...
Either way, that leaves us dudes in the dust!
Yeah, no thanks. No boys allowed with me!
Hey, y'all. Listen, I was in the Hideout...
And I couldn't tell who was who or what for that matter.
I thought they were demons, panicked and attacked them...
Whoa, was everyone okay after that...?!
Yo, we got lucky here. We're treatin' everyone's wounds right now.
And you, Megakin? You weren't attacked?
Nah, I'm all good. Just a few scratches.
You sound a lot worse off than that...
Yo, we gotta worry about that illusion right now.
It might make us lose focus and attack each other again.
It ain't cool. It ain't fair how it's doin' this to us and all these folks.
But we'd get our asses kicked if we go unprepared.
About Honey...
It sounded like Nyarlathotep can summon a bunch of demons at once to it too.
Yeah, we gotta take that thing down before it can cast its spell again...!
Copy!
There she is! Honey!
Honey!
*Wince*
>Honey falls to the ground after being hit by Nyarlathotep's attack.
Honey!
>Vince rushes to Honey's side, embraces her and tries calling to her.
Honey! Hang on, I'm right here!
*Pant*
She needs first aid.
I know! But human stuff doesn't work on her...!
Right, she's a Homunculus...!
>Honey's breathing grows weaker as she receives aid...
*Pant*
No...! This wound... I remember now...!
Was I...? Did I do this to her...?
It's... Okay...
Goddammit! How could I have been so blind?!
Vince...
She may be a Homunculus, but is dying in the same manner as a human would.
>Vince holds Honey tightly, but feels a violent urge well up.
You... You did this to her...

*Snicker*
Correct.
>As the girl answers, she begins morphing into Honey...!
You...! How big a piece of shit are you?!?!?!
Oh, why not ask yourself the same question? You were the one that could not tell who she was.

*Laugh*
Yes, such a wonderful expression! Let chaos reign once more!
No, it's about to cast its illusion again!
Honey... I'm...
It's okay... It looks like me, but its soul is still the same...
Be brave, Vince...
They're all our friends... All of them...
Even if they look different, I'm sure you'll be able to tell...
>The beating inside Honey's chest comes to a halt...
Ah, what sort of face will you make next?
>Nyarlathotep points its finger to the sky and casts its illusion again!
>Honey changes into a demon while still in Vince's arms.
>Vince tightly embraces the hideous demon.
Honey... I won't make the same mistake twice...
I can see now.
It looks like a demon, but it has Honey's soul. I'm sure of it.
>Vince can clearly sense Honey's presence within the demon.
>The Liberators arrive on the scene.
>But all you see are demons.
Crap! We get here just as it cast its spell again!
Where's Honey?!
Ugh, it's all just gross-ass demons!
Smell alone won't cut it anymore...
*Growl*
I can't tell if this is a demon or a person...!
That demon's face especially. I desperately wish to hit it...
Get ready.
Look around.
That demon's staring right at us...! Get ready to fight...!
>Just as the Liberators get ready to fight each other, someone yells at them all.
You guys are pathetic!
You can't even tell friend from foe?
Where's that precious bond you've been talking about?!
I can see now. I can see everything!
That voice...
Yes, we need to believe in each other. We're all friends...
We're... Friends...
>Everyone begins seeing past each other's demonic exteriors...
Shionyan! I knew it was you!
Well done. You upheld your duty as my servant.
Do you know who I am?!
Yes. A big, fat pig.
The very same!!
But she called you a pig...
Shiang Sun! Thank goodness! Can you see who I am?
Jeng Yun? Yes, I see that it's you.
Newbie! I came this close to shooting you just now...
Even as a demon, I felt compelled to shoot your face.
Rika! I knew it was you! You totally gave off this vibe, you know?
Phew... That was too close for comfort.
Yo, it's all thanks to Vince.
Yeah, and you know what comes next?
Aight. We gotta give Nyarlathotep what it deserves for what it did to Honey, y'all.
>Megakin and the others stare down the girl.
We see you. We know who you are now...!
Interesting. You've managed to see through my illusion.
I have no need to keep playing pretend then.
>The girl begins morphing into a vile demon unlike any other!
This is Nyarlathotep...?!
Now, have a taste of pure chaos!
>Your surroundings also being to warp and distort.
What the...? Are my eyes playing tricks on me...?
The sky and ground are starting to blend together...! Is this a part of its illusion too...?!
The ground becoming soft and rubbery...!
I... I can't keep my balance!
This is but a fraction of my true power. No human will be able to see through this.
Kneel before me! Watch as this world drowns in chaos!
>As everything falls into chaos and disarray,
>Nyarlathotep attacks the Liberators...!
